(text "NOTES:" (at 20.32 355.6 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 66ffce45-f94d-5b6d-ae70-09c92111cedc))
(text "EC enumerates to the x86 host as a plain USB device over Mu USB2_P3; firmware exposes keyboard/power/telemetry." (at 20.32 363.22 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 7010e283-8f33-50de-856b-a0a136f2982e))
(text "Touchscreen USB is separate on Mu USB2_P4; sheet 11 owns the retained Intehill USB-C touch/power path." (at 20.32 370.84 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 76d157e1-0c56-5601-95c5-958673d96d04))
(text "Trackpad uses Mu USB2_P8 as a direct internal USB HID pointing device; EC only owns reset/interrupt/sideband." (at 20.32 378.46 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 14827447-0331-5454-b1eb-499fe49d09aa))
(text "J51 and J55 are DNP alternate/service harnesses; sheets 10/11 own the real display video paths." (at 20.32 386.08 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 6f156181-dc4f-5408-a01f-51646881e5de))
(text "Fan PWM/tach are EC-owned. J52 uses fused 5V, 3.3V tach pull-up, and an open-drain PWM sink." (at 20.32 393.7 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid e4f4a84c-f0b7-57bb-81e2-5b8bd992a118))
(text "Thermal control has separate skin/hinge and Mu heatsink NTCs on ADC-capable EC pins." (at 20.32 401.32 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 9840ee37-e770-5e9f-acfb-193591c259b1))
(text "Cooling default is copper spreader/heatpipe/vapor chamber plus quiet blower; no Peltier/TEC in the base design." (at 20.32 408.94 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid 3ef78352-823e-5845-8945-b4ef8f1243b1))
(text "Solid-state AirJet-style modules are a future mechanical option, not the assumed electrical baseline." (at 20.32 416.56 0) (effects (font (size 1.27 1.27))) (uuid a1b9a9c9-5d89-51bf-9b29-2641197e211b))
